# Oversized File Discipline

These files are >300 lines. High regression risk. Surgical precision mandatory.

## High-Risk Registry
- `src/components/chat/ChatInput.tsx`
- `src/components/chat/FilePreviewModal.tsx`
- `src/components/chat/ArtifactPanel.tsx`
- `src/components/chat/ModelSelector.tsx`
- `src/components/chat/MessageBubble.tsx`
- `src-tauri/src/ipc/chat.rs`
- `src-tauri/src/ipc/models.rs`
- `src-tauri/src/voice.rs`

## Pre-Edit
- Use `grep`/`search` to locate the exact target region.
- Quote 3-5 lines of surrounding context to confirm location.
- State which lines/region will change BEFORE proposing the edit.

## Forbidden
- Output full file contents
- Reformat unrelated code (whitespace, imports, comments)
- "While I'm here" refactors of adjacent code
- Suggest splitting the file as part of the current task (note ONCE at end if relevant; do not act)

## Scope Limit
If an edit touches >50 lines, STOP and ask the user whether to proceed or scope differently.

## Post-Edit Verify
- No accidental import additions/removals
- No export changes
- Function signatures outside the edited region untouched
